00:26:28.700 --> 00:26:30.110 align:middle line:90%
So that's a big one.

00:26:30.110 --> 00:26:32.270 align:middle line:90%
Relationships-- it's huge.

00:26:32.270 --> 00:26:33.440 align:middle line:90%
Intimate relationships--

00:26:33.440 --> 00:26:34.430 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Huge.

00:26:34.430 --> 00:26:37.724 align:middle line:84%
>>NICK: Big all the time,
