>>LISA: If they are.

00:26:42.680 --> 00:26:44.000 align:middle line:90%
>>NICK: If they are-- exactly.

00:26:44.000 --> 00:26:46.290 align:middle line:90%
And then, weight loss.

00:26:46.290 --> 00:26:48.640 align:middle line:10%
It's an ongoing
issue-- really big.

00:26:48.640 --> 00:26:50.390 align:middle line:10%
And tapping works
