00:27:15.530 --> 00:27:17.780 align:middle line:84%
I think tapping is
so great for clarity.

00:27:17.780 --> 00:27:20.960 align:middle line:84%
Because the challenges
that I have now,

00:27:20.960 --> 00:27:23.180 align:middle line:84%
