00:27:33.850 --> 00:27:34.670 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Take care of your body.

00:27:34.670 --> 00:27:35.150 align:middle line:90%
>>NICK: Exactly.

00:27:35.150 --> 00:27:37.040 align:middle line:84%
So it's sort of this
internal conflict

00:27:37.040 --> 00:27:39.440 align:middle line:84%
