clarity not impulse,

00:27:47.330 --> 00:27:51.050 align:middle line:84%
or not feeling like I need
to do more or I'm not this

00:27:51.050 --> 00:27:52.010 align:middle line:90%
or I'm not that.

00:27:52.010 --> 00:27:55.422 align:middle line:84%
We often make decisions
from the insecure place.

00:27:55.422 --> 00:27:56.755 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: The over-achiever place.

00:27:56.755 --> 00:27:57.810 align:middle line:84%
>>NICK: The
over-achiever replace,

