00:29:01.580 --> 00:29:04.250 align:middle line:84%
is to really move the
needle on the stress

00:29:04.250 --> 00:29:05.210 align:middle line:90%
response in the body.

00:29:05.210 --> 00:29:07.236 align:middle line:90%
That is what it is proven to do.

00:29:07.236 --> 00:29:08.360 align:middle line:90%
>>NICK: Yeah, in a big way.

