But when--

00:29:29.150 --> 00:29:30.170 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It's an hour long class.

00:29:30.170 --> 00:29:31.550 align:middle line:90%
>>NICK: It's an hour long class.

00:29:31.550 --> 00:29:33.091 align:middle line:84%
But when you do the
tapping, when you

00:29:33.091 --> 00:29:34.490 align:middle line:90%
get to the underlying stuff--

00:29:34.490 --> 00:29:35.750 align:middle line:90%
and yoga can do that as well.

00:29:35.750 --> 00:29:37.295 align:middle line:84%
Yoga can get to the
underlying stuff.

