You go deep enough,
you clean stuff up.

00:29:39.380 --> 00:29:42.170 align:middle line:10%
But the tapping can very quickly
get to the underlying stuff,

00:29:42.170 --> 00:29:44.960 align:middle line:10%
so the stress just doesn't
naturally come up again.

00:29:44.960 --> 00:29:47.850 align:middle line:10%
