00:29:48.650 --> 00:29:51.140 align:middle line:84%
The external environment
might not have changed,

00:29:51.140 --> 00:29:53.930 align:middle line:84%
but you've retrain the
way your mind reacts.

00:29:53.930 --> 00:29:56.720 align:middle line:84%
So you can be a zen monk
about the situation,

00:29:56.720 --> 00:29:58.597 align:middle line:84%
or just take a
different perspective.

00:29:58.597 --> 00:30:00.680 align:middle line:84%
And that's what I've found
has happened in my life

00:30:00.680 --> 00:30:03.560 align:middle line:84%
and I've seen it happen
in the lives of thousands

00:30:03.560 --> 00:30:04.860 align:middle line:90%
